      <title>委内瑞拉在选举支出狂潮中增加美元供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/venezuela-boosts-dollar-supply-amid-election-spending-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉政府正在增加美元销售，以抑制尼古拉斯·马杜罗总统竞选支出造成的通胀影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/venezuela-boosts-dollar-supply-amid-election-spending-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 18:24:51 GMT</pubDate>
